OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772283793
OL,3,CPolice hunt for man after child
OL,4,Csuffers life-changing injuries in hit-
OL,5,Cand-run
OL,7,FPolice are searching for a 33-year-old
OL,8,Fman after a child was left with
OL,9,F"serious and potentially life-changing
OL,10,Finjuries" following a hit-and-run in
OL,11,FReading.
OL,13,FThames Valley Police has launched an
OL,14,Furgent appeal to locate Matthew
OL,15,FHaylett in connection with the
OL,16,Fcollision, which occurred yesterday
OL,17,F(Thursday, 26 February) on Rushey Way
OL,18,Fin Lower Earley.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
