PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772283793
OL,3,CPolice hunt for man after child
OL,4,Csuffers life-changing injuries in hit-
OL,5,Cand-run
OL,7,FOfficers say a van collided with metal
OL,8,Fbarriers and struck the child, who
OL,9,Fremains in hospital receiving
OL,10,Ftreatment.
OL,12,FInvestigators believe Haylett may be
OL,13,Fusing the alias Matthew Harris.
OL,15,FHe is described as a white man with
OL,16,Fblack hair and a black beard. He was
OL,17,Flast seen wearing a baseball cap and
OL,18,Fdark clothing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772283793
OL,3,CPolice hunt for man after child
OL,4,Csuffers life-changing injuries in hit-
OL,5,Cand-run
OL,7,FSergeant Matt Cadmore, the
OL,8,Finvestigating officer, said: "We're
OL,9,Furging anyone with any information
OL,10,Fabout Matthew's whereabouts to please
OL,11,Fcome forward and speak to us.
OL,13,F"No matter how small, every detail
OL,14,Fmight help us to locate him."
OL,16,FThe force is also appealing for anyone
OL,17,Fwho may have CCTV or dashcam footage
OL,18,Fof the collision, or the moments
OL,19,Fleading up to it, to come forward.
OL,26,@pD@^OUuD@AOUvD@]O]
