OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772283793
OL,3,CPolice hunt for man after child
OL,4,Csuffers life-changing injuries in hit-
OL,5,Cand-run
OL,7,FMembers of the public are advised not
OL,8,Fto approach Haylett if they see him,
OL,9,Fbut to call 999 immediately, quoting
OL,10,Freference 43260097181.
OL,12,FAlternatively, those with information
OL,13,Fcan contact the independent charity
OL,14,FCrimestoppers 100% anonymously on 0800
OL,15,F555 111.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
